Feature:: Add employee to activity
    Description: The project manager
    adds an employee to an activity
    Actor: Project Manager
# Main scenario
Scenario:
    Given there is a project
    And employee with ID "mkr" is logged
    in
    And "mkr" is the project manager
    Given there is another employee
    And has "20" or less ongoing
    activities
    When add employee to project
    activity
    Then employee is added to the
    project activity
# Alternative scenario
Scenario:
    Given there is a project
    And employee with ID "mkr" is logged in
    And "mkr" is the project manager
    Given there is another employee
    And has more than "20" ongoing
    activities
    When add employee to project
    activity
    Then the error message "Employee too
    busy" is given